values: My family is moving to Wichita and I hope they stay safe.

Dear Friends,

I hope that your summer has been a good one, as mine wasn't. I hope that your year goes great as mine is going to be hell on earth. I hope you guys enjoy every minute of rp, and chatting with friends, as I am going to wait and see weather or not I am going to see my mother again. 

To all of you guys, I wish you the best in everything, as I finish my senior year in college. *waves to all and fades*

P.S.

Rain drops and falls, but it never falls or drops in the same way.

The time we have in this world is short. That what you have and hold it close to your heart and soul. Remember that everything is just just a arms length away. Don't back down from anything no matter what. Stay close to friends and love ones and don't take anythign for granted. Stay strong is what you believe in and hope to God or whoever you believe in to be the God of Gods. Be positive in everything and everything will come to you in the end.

Mircales happen everyday and the light around the rainbow shines on you sometimes, so be happy that you are live and ready to see the world.


Sincerely to all,
sessinulvr

The days and mouths unhold as we move on with our lives. We try to make it clear that we live in a world of peace and safety. We try to live in what we imagine the world to be, as other people move around you like chess pieces moving across the board. The world is never what you think, as I think that even the nicest people do things that you never would ever find. But spring break is a nice little week that we can relax and just say forget the world and just live it out. I say to just relax and let life flow to whatever.

Life is life, peace is peace.

*winks*
Jen

What can you say when you have given your all to a father that doesn't love you back..What can you say to a father that doesn't give a FUCK about your family..What can you say about how it is reacting to my mother..How can you do this my our family..How can you my father say that after 23 years of marriage to mother that it was all a prison and that you where trapped..How can you say this to us..How..Why..are you breaking up the family.. Just tell me why you are doing this to us..Why are you leaving mother...Why are you giving up everyone that truly loves you for who you are. How can you tell mother that you want a divorce...Dad!!! Why are you killing us..Why are you doing this...WHY!!!!!!!!!!!...

Do we mean anything to you..Do you even care..Do you even hear us try to talk to you asking you to come back into our lives...Why dad are you being a bloodly,basturd, son-a-bitch, coward to mom..She loves you and you don't even want to relieve that...

Dad.....

I hope you go to hell!!!!!!!!!!!!!!


Sorry about this but I just had to type something out for what just happened in the last two weeks..
It is a sad day for me..May favorite site is down and I can't get in..*sniffles*

The day of finals have come to me and my fellow classmates. We are studying and studying for the days of days..Next mouth is going to be it..The few days we have to spend free are the ones that I am going to spend on studying my arse off..I would, wish I didn't have to take them..I would be happy, but poor me I do..*shrugs* Life sucks when you are in college.

BLAH!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!

Was does the day have to be so boring and long.


BLAH BLAH BLAH
